summary:
Mathematician and English teacher. 
Strong operations professional with a bachelor's in Mathematics, from the Aegean University and the 168 hours TEFL level 5 certificate from The Tefl Academy. Also, a Diploma focused in Meteorology and Forecasting from Hellenic National Meteorological Service.
Senior R & D  Technician, with a demonstrated history of working in the medical device industry. 
Skilled in Teaching English as a second language, Teaching Maths(primary and high school level) Medical Devices,  Process development, Problem-solving, Employee Training, ISO 13485, QMS documentation, Six lean sigmas,  Mechanical test execution, Valve performance testing, Project Management, Quality control of products (VI and QA documentation) , NCs and CAPAs, Production planning.
